  <div xml:id="PN273">
<lg type="edition">
<l>māvā rātē māvā rātē</l>
<l>yellār māvum vantaṉa vemmiṟ</l>
<l>pulluḷaik kuṭumip putalvaṟ ṟanta</l>
<l>celva ṉūru māvā rātē</l>
<l>yirupēr yāṟṟa voruperuṅ kūṭal</l>
<l>vilaṅkiṭu perumaram pōla</l>
<l>vulantaṉṟu kollavaṉ malainta māvē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>[His] horse did not come. [His] horse did not come.</l>
<l>Everyone’s horses came. The horse </l>
<l>[our] lord rides who has given a son, with a tuft of short hair,</l>
<l>to our house did not come.</l>
<l>As a huge tree put across</l>
<l>two big rivers’ one vast confluence,</l>
<l>is it dead, the horse that bore him?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
